<!-- ============================================================
     ADMIN DASHBOARD  |  Owner: Rainie (Student E)

     Admin only -- the route needs checkAuthenticated AND checkAdmin.

     The admin is an operator, not one of our target users. Two jobs:

       1. Manage user accounts
          List users, search/filter them, and deactivate an account
          by setting users.is_active = 0.
          Deactivate, do NOT delete: deleting a user CASCADES and
          destroys their whole collection. Login already checks
          is_active, so setting it to 0 locks them out immediately.

       2. Curate the reference lists  (genres, conditions)
          These are what make Zhan Fung's filtering work -- free text
          cannot be filtered reliably. CRUD on both.
          Deleting a genre still used by cards is blocked by the
          database (ER_ROW_IS_REFERENCED_2). Catch it and show a
          friendly message rather than a crash.

     Renders with: user, users  (+ genres / conditions for the lists)
